org.apache.paimon.flink.sink

Class StoreSinkWriteState

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.flink.sink.StoreSinkWriteState

  • public class StoreSinkWriteState
extends Object
    States for StoreSinkWrites.

    States are positioned first by table name and then by key name. This class should be initiated in a sink operator and then given to StoreSinkWrite.
